  m_text: 'This game is a fan remake of the Kessel Sabacc card game from Star Wars:
    Outlaws, developed by Massive Entertainment and published by Ubisoft. All credit
    for the game rules belongs to those talented game creators. Addtionally, I do
    not own any legal rights to Star Wars or Star Wars licenses.


    I made this
    game because I enjoy playing Kessel Sabacc in Star Wars: Outlaws, and I wanted
    to recreate a similar experience as the UNO game also published by Ubisoft.


    Thank
    you for playing.'
